Item 9. Regulation FD Disclosure
 
On January 26, 2004, Baxter International Inc. issued the attached press release announcing the resignation of Harry M. Jansen Kraemer, Jr., as Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of the company. The press release is furnished as Exhibit 99 and incorporated herein by reference.
 
 
