Item 9. Regulation FD Disclosure
 
On June 21, 2004, Baxter International Inc. issued the attached press release announcing the election of John Greisch as senior vice president and chief financial officer of the company. The press release is furnished as Exhibit 99 and incorporated herein by reference.
 
Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned thereunto duly authorized.
 
 
