(10) days' written notice mailed to the Guarantor by ordinary mail at its address referred to in shall be deemed reasonable notice of any matters contained in such notice. The Guarantor consents and agrees that neither the Agent nor the Banks shall be under any obligation to marshall any assets in favor of the Guarantor or against or in payment of any or all of the Guaranteed Obligations.
