3.02
Denominations.
     Unless otherwise provided as contemplated by with respect to any series of Securities, and except as provided in , the Securities of each series shall be issuable in denominations of $1,000 and any integral multiple thereof. Securities of each series shall be numbered, lettered or otherwise distinguished in such manner or in accordance with such plan as the Authorized Officers executing the same may determine with the reasonable approval of the Trustee.
