The Purchaser shall allow, and shall procure that the relevant Group Company allows, the Seller and its advisers to reasonably investigate the matter or circumstance alleged to give rise to a claim; and
 
The Purchaser shall, and the Purchaser shall procure that any other members of the Purchaser's Group shall, at the Seller's expense, give all such information and assistance as the Seller may reasonably request, including such professional or legal advisers as the Seller may nominate, in connection with the Seller's participation in the defense of any such third party claims.
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
