SECTION 2.06. . Unless previously terminated, the Commitments shall terminate immediately upon the first to occur of the following: (i) the Closing Date (after giving effect to the Borrowing on such date), (ii) the termination of the Borrower's obligation to consummate the Acquisition pursuant to the Share Purchase Agreement, and (iii) the Commitment Termination Date. Any such termination of the Commitments shall be permanent.
